      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver for those who aren't concerned with cosmetic perfection. The exterior shows clear signs of age, including several noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and some paint fading on the hood and roof. Inside, the cabin exhibits moderate wear on the seats and carpets, though all primary features and controls are functioning as intended. While it remains mechanically sound for everyday use, a buyer should expect the typical maintenance needs associated with a well-used vehicle of this age.",
