      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty ride. It\u2019s been super reliable and is still in great shape for its next adventure! It runs smoothly, has been well-loved, and is ready to hit the road today. I\u2019ve priced it to sell because I\u2019m looking for a quick, easy handoff. Feel free to ask any questions\u2014I'm happy to help!",
