    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 996-generation Carrera 2 is a driver-focused example featuring the 3.6L M96 flat-six paired with a G96 6-speed manual transaxle. The powertrain has been reinforced with a dual-row IMS bearing retrofit and a preventative RMS replacement. The suspension geometry is maintained via fresh control arms and Bilstein B6 dampers, ensuring crisp turn-in and high-speed stability. Recent service includes a full cooling system refresh and a borescope inspection confirming zero bore scoring. While the finish shows minor road-going patina, the mechanical vitals\u2014including oil pressure and compression across all cylinders\u2014are within factory specifications. This is a mechanically sorted 911 optimized for the purist.",
      "price": 31800.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used vehicle in good condition. Regularly maintained. Clean title. Reliable performance. No mechanical issues.",
